1.LCM AND HCF 
----------------------------------------

x=a=int(input("FIRST NUMBER "))
y=b=int(input("SECOND NUMBER "))
while(y):
    x,y=y,x%y
hcf=x
print("hcf is ",hcf)
print("lcm is ",(a*b)/hcf)

OUT:
FIRST NUMBER 2
SECOND NUMBER 4
hcf is  2
lcm is  4.0
